<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>사용방법 안내 - GS THE POP</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css"> 
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<!-- fullpop :: 사용방법 안내  -->
	<div id="pop01" class="fullPop">
		<a href="#" class="btnHome">홈으로 이동</a>
		<h1>사용방법 안내</h1>
		<div class="popCon">
			<div class="guideContainer line">
				<h2 class="titDep1">유료 멤버십 사용 안내</h2>
				<p class="guideTxt">사용중인 유료 멤버십을 선택하여 사용하실 수 있습니다.</p>
				<ol class="iconStepList useGuide">
					<li>
						<strong class="tit">STEP 01</strong>
						<span class="txt">MY유료 멤버십 상품을 선택해주세요.</span>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong class="tit">STEP 02</strong>
						<span class="txt">QR담기를 ON으로 선택해주세요.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="icoPnum">
						<strong class="tit">STEP 03</strong>
						<span class="txt">다중 상품 선택일 경우 QR메인에서 상품을 선택하세요.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="icoPnum">
						<strong class="tit">STEP 04</strong>
						<span class="txt">상품을 계산대에 제시해 주세요.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="icoPnum">
						<strong class="tit">STEP 05</strong>
						<span class="txt">QR코드를 스캔하여 상품 결제를 진행해 주세요.</span>
					</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
			<div class="guideContainer line">
				<h2 class="titDep1">상품 교환 안내(매장용)</h2>
				<ol class="iconStepList prChangeGuide">
					<li>
						<strong class="tit">STEP 01</strong>
						<span class="txt">유료 멤버십 대상 상품을 스캔하세요.</span>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong class="tit">STEP 02</strong>
						<span class="txt">유료 멤버십 QR코드를 스캔하세요.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="icoPnum">
						<strong class="tit">STEP 03</strong>
						<span class="txt">상품을 고객님께 전달해 주세요.</span>
					</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
		</div>
		<button type="button" class="btnClose">팝업 닫기</button>
	</div>
	<!-- //fullpop :: 사용방법 안내  -->
</body>
</html>

